beer.beer_description: Pine-a-Pils Pineapple Pilsner was designed by and brewed in partnership with our mates at The Nobel Hops. A 4.3% ABV lager with a simple malt base of Pilsner, Wheat and Carapils that makes for the ultimate summer crusher. The addition of fresh pineapple and a nice whack of Australian Vic Secret hops presents a lovely hit of tropical fruit and citrus with a clean, smooth finish.
